These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, action
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster  | action |
| Transport     | snowmobile | skateboard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: broccoli, nectarine
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, golf
1. the person eating nectarine is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Food    | broccoli      | nectarine         |
| Sport   | rowing | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea
There 2 different types of food: cherry, nectarine
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | water   |
| Food       | nectarine  | cherry |

 #################################

 
